@section Displays Submenu
@cindex displays submenu

In the main menu, found by clicking @kbd{mouse-3}, a submenu labeled
"Displays" is available.  This submenu lets you easily choose between
different display modes in speedbar.

This menu only contains modes currently loaded into emacs.  By default,
this would include Files, Quick Buffers, and Buffers.  Other major
display modes, such as Info are loaded separately.

