@chapter File Mode
@cindex file mode

The most common mode for speedbar is Files Mode.  In this mode,
directories, files, and file tags can all be manipulated in a clean tree
form.

@menu
* Directory Display::   What the display means.
* File Keybindings::    Performing file operations.
